findings.message:
Reentrancy in CToken.redeemFresh(address,uint256,uint256) (Comptroller.sol#1304-1373):
	External calls:
	- allowed = comptroller.redeemAllowed(address(this),redeemer,redeemTokens) (Comptroller.sol#1332)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- totalSupply = totalSupply - redeemTokens (Comptroller.sol#1356)
	CTokenStorage.totalSupply (Comptroller.sol#385) can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- CToken.exchangeRateStoredInternal() (Comptroller.sol#1105-1124)
	- CTokenStorage.totalSupply (Comptroller.sol#385)
findings.name: reentrancy-no-eth

findings.message:
Reentrancy in CToken.liquidateBorrowInternal(address,uint256,CTokenInterface) (Comptroller.sol#1536-1551):
	External calls:
	- error = cTokenCollateral.accrueInterest() (Comptroller.sol#1543)
	- liquidateBorrowFresh(msg.sender,borrower,repayAmount,cTokenCollateral) (Comptroller.sol#1550)
		- allowed = comptroller.liquidateBorrowAllowed(address(this),address(cTokenCollateral),liquidator,borrower,repayAmount) (Comptroller.sol#1563)
		- allowed = comptroller.repayBorrowAllowed(address(this),payer,borrower,repayAmount) (Comptroller.sol#1481)
		- allowed = comptroller.seizeAllowed(address(this),seizerToken,liquidator,borrower,seizeTokens) (Comptroller.sol#1644)
		- require(bool,string)(cTokenCollateral.seize(liquidator,borrower,seizeTokens) == NO_ERROR,token seizure failed) (Comptroller.sol#1611)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- liquidateBorrowFresh(msg.sender,borrower,repayAmount,cTokenCollateral) (Comptroller.sol#1550)
		- totalBorrows = totalBorrowsNew (Comptroller.sol#1521)
	CTokenStorage.totalBorrows (Comptroller.sol#375) can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- CToken.accrueInterest() (Comptroller.sol#1139-1191)
	- CToken.borrowRatePerBlock() (Comptroller.sol#1019-1021)
	- CToken.exchangeRateStoredInternal() (Comptroller.sol#1105-1124)
	- CToken.supplyRatePerBlock() (Comptroller.sol#1027-1029)
	- CTokenStorage.totalBorrows (Comptroller.sol#375)
	- liquidateBorrowFresh(msg.sender,borrower,repayAmount,cTokenCollateral) (Comptroller.sol#1550)
		- totalReserves = totalReservesNew (Comptroller.sol#1671)
	CTokenStorage.totalReserves (Comptroller.sol#380) can be used in cross function reentrancies:
	- CToken.accrueInterest() (Comptroller.sol#1139-1191)
	- CToken.borrowRatePerBlock() (Comptroller.sol#1019-1021)
	- CToken.exchangeRateStoredInternal() (Comptroller.sol#1105-1124)
	- CToken.supplyRatePerBlock() (Comptroller.sol#1027-1029)
	- CTokenStorage.totalReserves (Comptroller.sol#380)
findings.name: reentrancy-no-eth
